welcome_description:
Qedela lesi sifundo esifushane ukuze uthole ibhonasi yokwamukela ekhethekile.

Kuzothatha umzuzu nje!
free_spins_description:
Nsuku zonke noma isonto ungena ngemvume, i-akhawunti yakho izoklonyeliswa nsuku zonke 'Ama-Spins Amahhala' kanye 'nama-Mystery Boxes' masonto onke.

Inombolo oyitholayo incike ezingeni le-akhawunti yakho.
daily_streak_description:
Nsuku zonke ungena ngemvume futhi uzuze inani elincane lezinhlamvu zemali, ungafuna ukulandelana kwakho kwansuku zonke.

Izinsuku eziningi ezilandelanayo ufuna ukuphumelela kwakho, umvuzo uba mkhulu!

Amaleveli e-akhawunti aphezulu nawo athola imiklomelo emikhulu.
ptc_ads_description:
Buka Izikhangiso ze-PTC ukuze uthole izikhangiso ezisheshayo, ezimfushane ukuze uthuthukise inani lakho lemali yansuku zonke.

Isikhangiso sizovuleka kuthebhu entsha, ngakho qiniseka ukuthi sihlala sivuliwe kuze kuphele isibali sikhathi!
missions_description:
Uzothola amakhulukhulu emishini nezimfuno okumele uziqedele esigabeni esithi 'Izinjongo' sewebhusayithi.

Ukuqedela ohambweni kanye nezimfuno kuyindlela enhle yokuthola Izinhlamvu zemali zebhonasi.

Hlola ikhasi elithi Thola → 'Imisebenzi Yebhonasi' ukuze uthole imininingwane.
offers_description:
Ukuqedela okunikezwayo kungenye yezindlela ezinhle kakhulu zokuthola Izinhlamvu zemali ku-GigaFaucet.

Okunikezwayo kungatholakala esigabeni esithi 'Hola' sewebhusayithi.

Kunezinhlobo eziningi ezahlukene zokunikezwayo ezitholakalayo. Qiniseka ukuthi uyawahlolela lawo akusebenzela kangcono.
xp_description:
Ngaso sonke isikhathi uma uqedela okunikezwayo, dlala isiphindaphindi, noma ubuka ividiyo, njll., uzozuza i-XP (Amaphuzu Okuhlangenwe nakho).

Ukuzuza i-XP kuzonyusa izinga le-akhawunti yakho, kuvule izici ezengeziwe nemiklomelo emikhulu.

Ungathola ileveli ye-akhawunti yakho ekhasini lakho lephrofayela noma lamabhonasi.
withdraw_description:
Ungakwazi ukuhoxisa Izinhlamvu zemali zakho uma usufinyelele ubuncane bezinhlamvu zemali ezingu-30,000.

Ukuze uhoxise, yiya ku-Akhawunti → 'I-Cash Out' bese ukhetha indlela yokuhoxa oyikhethayo.

Landela imiyalelo ukuze uqedele ukukhipha kwakho.
all_set_description:
Manje usukulungele ukuqala ukuthola izinhlamvu zemali ku-GigaFaucet!

Khumbula ukuhlola nsuku zonke ukuthola ama-bonus spins akho namabhokisi emfihlakalo, bese uqedela okunikezwayo kanye nemisebenzi yokwandisa imali yakho engenayo.

Inhlanhla futhi ujabule!
